title: Multiplying the Numerator and Denominator
text: We can multiply the numerators to get $$90$$ and the denominators to get $$120$$. Thus, we have $$\frac{90}{120}$$.

title: Simplifying if Necessary
text: $$\frac{90}{120}$$ can be simplified to $$\frac{9}{12}$$, which can in turn be simplified to $$\frac{3}{4}$$
